      "reviewed": true,
      "display_order": 5,
      "explanation": "Ser (to be): soc, ets, és, som, sou, són. Since the 2016 spelling reform, soc has no accent — but és and són keep theirs to stay distinct from other words. Professions take no article: ella és professora.",
      "culture_note": "",
      "references": [
        {
          "title": "Wiktionary: ser (Catalan)",
          "url": "https://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/ser#Catalan"
