    {
      "title": "-re and -ir verbs (perdre, dormir, llegir)",
      "level": "A1",
      "function": "Sleep, read, hear — the other families",
      "source": "contributor",
      "reviewed": true,
      "display_order": 8,
      "explanation": "-re verbs: perdre → perdo, perds, perd, perdem, perdeu, perden. -ir verbs come plain (dormir → dormo) or with -eix- in the singular and third plural (llegir → llegeixo, llegeixes, llegeix… but llegim, llegiu). Preferir takes -eix- too.",
      "culture_note": "",
